{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_09_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 この筋肉と一緒なら",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "教えてくれ。愛から見て\n莉央さんや葵、こころの頑張りは足りていないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me. From your perspective‚ Ai‚\nare Rio-san‚ Aoi‚ and Kokoro not working hard enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、そんなことありません！！\nみんな、すっごく頑張ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not at all!!\nEveryone is working super hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺もそう思う。なら不調の原因は努力不足じゃない\n他の所に原因があるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think so too. Then the reason of bad condition isn’t from a lack of effort.\nMaybe the cause lies somewhere else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "他の所、ですか。そういえば、莉央さんと葵さんは\nリズノワらしさについて、気にしてましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Somewhere else? Come to think of it‚ Rio-san and Aoi-san\nwere worried about “what it means to be LizNoir”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワらしさ、か\n愛が思うリズノワらしさって、なんなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“What it means to be LizNoir‚” huh?\nWhat do you think it means to be LizNoir‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "辛い時、一人じゃ頑張れない時\n励ましてくれる力強さです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the strength to encourage you\nwhen you’re struggling alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私、練習生時代はずっとリズノワに励まされてきました\nだから今度は私が、沢山の人を励ましたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was a trainee‚ LizNoir always encouraged me.\nSo now‚ I want to encourage a lot of people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5192277836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今のリズノワは、愛が望んでいるとおり\nファンのみんなを励ませているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is LizNoir now encouraging their fans\nthe way you want them to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！　リズノワのライブの観客席はいつも\n笑顔で一杯なんですから。それだけは自信があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! The audience at LizNoir’s live performances\nis always full of smiles. I’m confident about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "観てくれる人を励まして、元気にすること\nそれが私にとってのアイドルらしさで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To encourage and energize the people watching…\nthat’s what being an idol means to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そっか。私、大切なものが見えてませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ I see. I wasn’t looking at what’s important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1327657859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "いつもステージの上から\nファンの人達の笑顔を沢山見てるのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I’m always looking at\nall the smiling faces of the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、目に見える成果がないだなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But to say that there are no visible results…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4695236365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。そんなことを言ったら、ファンの人達に失礼だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It would be disrespectful to the fans to say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5824940522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。それに、これだけ長い間活動していれば\n簡単に解決出来ない問題だって出てきますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. Besides‚ if we’re active for such a long time‚\nthere will be problems that aren’t easily solved‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "今、私達が抱えてる問題は、きっとすぐに解決しないし\nこれからも悩み続けるんだろうなって、思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problems we’re facing now probably won’t be solved immediately‚\nand I think we’ll continue to worry about them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6333302816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これからは変に思い詰めたりしません\n私は私に出来ることをしようと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But from now on‚ I won’t dwell on things too much.\nI’m going to do what I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "出来ること？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What you can do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6546008269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "確かに今のリズノワは行き詰まってるのかもしれません\nだから、問題が解決出来るその日まで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that LizNoir might be at an impasse right now.\nSo until the day we can solve our problems‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが悩んで、苦しんでいる時は\n私がリズノワのみんなを励まします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when everyone is worried and suffering‚\nI will encourage everyone in LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　自分がやるべきことが\n分かりました。さぁ、すっきりしたところで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I understand what I have to do.\nNow‚ with a clear head――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "全快までトレーニングは禁止だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re forbidden from training until you’re fully recovered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1900967636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　そんなー！　…………ぷっ、あはは\n全部お見通しですね。まずは体を治すことに専念します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh!? No way~! ……Pfft‚ ahaha.\nYou see right through me. I’ll focus on getting better first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2278388149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――復帰後のライブイベント",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Live Event After Recovery",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.2793713926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.1127047259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.1793769875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげですっかり元気です\nその節はありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m completely healthy now thanks to {user}-san.\nThank you so much for that time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.8266343473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、東京シーサイドでイベントを\nやらせてもらえるなんて、思ってませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I never thought\nwe’d get to do an event at Tokyo Seaside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "先方からのたっての希望なんだ\n……ほら、ここにも、リズノワが挙げた成果があるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They specifically requested us.\n…See? Here’s another result of LizNoir’s hard work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.5000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.6372686742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……。私、目が曇ってました\n目の前のことさえ、見えてませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right… I was blind.\nI couldn’t even see what was right in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.6000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.4123479562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。今日は私達の力強い姿を\n精一杯、見せつけてきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san. Today‚ I’m going to show everyone\nour strong side with everything I’ve got.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ってる人には応援を、踏み出せない人には勇気を\n怖いことや苦しいこともあるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Encouragement to the striving‚ courage to the hesitant.\nEven though there are scary and painful things‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 217.5253869094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "頑張るのって楽しいんだよって\n勇気を出そうって、伝えたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to tell them that working hard is fun‚\nand to be brave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.1333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、俺も応援してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I’m cheering for you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.7519175248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.7525751151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　伝えてきます！\n私のパフォーマンスと、筋肉で！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! I’ll make sure to get that message across!\nWith my performance‚ and my muscles!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.0333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　待ってくれ、また迷走してないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Hold on‚ are you going off on a tangent again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.5769064145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.2402171172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ることは苦しいだけじゃなく楽しい！\nこれって、筋トレと同じなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Working hard isn’t just painful‚ it’s fun!\nIt’s the same as muscle training!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.5666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 240.1305115736
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "そして、結果へと繋がり、体を支える力になる\nまさに筋肉は、私が伝えたいことを体現してるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It leads to results‚ and becomes the strength to support your body.\nMuscles perfectly embody what I want to convey!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai026.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのことも支えてみせますよー！　こころと私の\n意見が割れた時、先輩達が信じて支えてくれたみたいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll support LizNoir too! Like when Kokoro and I\ndisagreed‚ our seniors trusted and supported us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.7367360468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 258.5146157618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。急に筋肉とか言い出すから\n少し驚いたけど……その意気だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. I was a little surprised\nthat you brought up muscles so suddenly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.1666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "愛はもうリズノワの端っこじゃない。リズノワを支える\n立派な柱だ。……おっと、そろそろ出番だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you’re not on the edge of LizNoir anymore. You’re a fine pillar\nthat supports LizNoir. …Oh‚ it’s almost our turn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.4666681926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6207.970869999997,
          "startTime": 272.0333348592
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai027.m4a",
      "text": "はい、行ってきます！　ステージ、楽しんできますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’m off! I’ll enjoy the stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.3274046615,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
