        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 276.3274046615
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 281.8104431346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai028.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　私達のCM、観てくれましたかー？\n実は私、最近少し悩んでいたことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone~! Did you see our CM?\nActually‚ I was struggling with something recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.8666681926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4372.893250399955,
          "startTime": 287.233336385
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai029.m4a",
      "text": "でも今日、ここに集まってくれた\nみんなの笑顔を見たら、吹っ切れちゃいました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But seeing the smiles of\neveryone here today blew it all away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.0000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai030.m4a",
      "text": "頑張るって楽しい\nどんな悩みだって、楽しんで乗り越えられる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Working hard is fun.\nWe can overcome any obstacle if we enjoy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.5333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_03-ai031.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと、この筋肉と一緒なら！\nさぁ！　暑さに負けないくらい楽しんじゃいましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m with all of you‚ and these muscles!\nNow! Let’s have so much fun that we don’t even notice the heat!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.6000015259,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
